     I                                        1  120WTMDT
     I                                        1   60WTIME
     I                                        7  120WDATE
TCHK8I                                        7   80WDAYY
TCHK8I                                        9  100WDAMM
TCHK8I                                       11  120WDADD
      * DELETE DATE(YYYYMMDD) PART MASTER
     I            DS
