     C                     ENDSR
TCHK3C***********************************************************
TCHK3C* MOVE(SET QTY. FOR NOT WORKING DAY)
TCHK3C***********************************************************
TCHK3C*          @MOVE     BEGSR
TCHK3C**
TCHK3C*                    Z-ADD*ZERO     WSUMQ
TCHK3C*          *IN92     DOUEQ'1'
TCHK3C*          AFDLDT    ORGT WRDAT
TCHK3C**
TCHK3C**REQUESTED CUM - SHIPPED CUM=VARIANCE
TCHK3C**VARIANCE - SUM.NOT WORKING DAY ORDER QTY.=THIS DAY ORDER QTY.
TCHK3C**THIS DAY ORDER QTY. + SUM. QTY
TCHK3C*          AFQTY2    SUB  AFYSQY    WQTY2
TCHK3C*          WQTY2     IFGT *ZERO
TCHK3C*          WQTY2     SUB  WSUMQ     WQTY3
TCHK3C*                    ADD  WQTY3     WSUMQ
TCHK3C*                    END
TCHK3C**
TCHK3C*          KEY5      READEABF2P011                 92
TCHK3C*                    END
TCHK3C**
TCHK3C*          WSUMQ     IFGT *ZERO
TCHK3C*                    Z-ADDWQTY3     WQTY2
TCHK3C*                    MOVE WQTY3     WSURY
TCHK3C**
TCHK3C*                    ELSE
TCHK3C*                    Z-ADD*ZERO     WQTY2
TCHK3C*                    END
TCHK3C**
TCHK3C*                    ENDSR
